Add a filter to the index view of the superheroes. This will allow the visitor to search for an existing superpower and display all the superheroes with that superpower on the same view page.

Hints / Tips
If you're having a hard time implementing the filter, take a look at this http://guides.rubyonrails.org/form_helpers.html#a-generic-search-form. We are asking an input field to search for superpowers.


